      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 is a high-revving icon featuring the S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a crisp Getrag six-speed manual gearbox and a mechanical M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis has been maintained for rigidity, including essential subframe reinforcement and updated suspension bushings to preserve its legendary handling precision. While the exterior displays minor road wear consistent with its status as a dedicated driver's car, the mechanical vitals are robust, offering linear power delivery all the way to its 8,000 RPM redline. An exceptional opportunity for an enthusiast seeking a visceral, naturally aspirated performance machine with sorted underpinnings.",
