      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a well-preserved example that strikes a perfect balance between a daily driver and a pride-of-ownership machine. The exterior paint still holds a brilliant luster, though upon close inspection, you will find a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the passenger-side mirror housing\u2014typical marks of a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. The body panels are straight with consistent gaps throughout. Inside, the cabin remains a comfortable and clean environment. The premium upholstery shows light character creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster, but remains free of tears or heavy stains. All interior technology, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium audio system, is fully operational. Under the hood, the engine bay is clean and shows signs of diligent maintenance; the car starts promptly, idles smoothly, and pulls through the gears without hesitation. Recent service includes a fresh oil change, a coolant flush, and a multi-point inspection confirming the brakes and suspension are in solid working order. It comes with a complete set of floor mats and a documented service history for the past three years.",
